  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims at improving the working conditions in mining industry in Peru. The focus is to create a strong national level trade union for the mining sector that will defend particularly the rights of sub-contracted workers. Other objectives of the project are to train union leaders, recruit new members and campaign to eliminate the employer&#xC2;&#xB4;s right to intermediate in the collection of trade union fees.</narrative>
